high_descs: Turn around and walk to the green table on the right.
Pick up the tomato to the left of the pan on the table.
Turn around and walk to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink, rinse it for a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn around and walk to the green table.
Put the rinsed tomato in front of the salt shaker to the right of the green sponge on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed tomato on a table.

high_descs: turn around and move to the green table on the right, turn to the right to face the table in front of the tomato
pick the tomato up off of the table
turn around and move to forward to face the sink
put the tomato in to the sink, turn the water on to wash off the tomato, turn the water off and remove the tomato from the sink
turn around and move forward back to the table with the green top
put the tomato on the table
anns.task_desc: put a clean tomato on to the table

high_descs: Turn around and face the island on the right.
Pick up the tomato from the front of the counter.
Hold the tomato and turn around to the sink.
Put the tomato in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the tomato.
Hold the tomato and turn around to the island.
Place the tomato on the counter, in front of the salt.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a tomato and place it on the counter.
